Package bibliothek.gui.dock.station.toolbar.layer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SideSnapDropLayer
    Describes the area around a ToolbarDockStation where the user can drop a Dockable into.
    ToolbarContainerDropLayer
    A DockStationDropLayer describing the region around a ToolbarContainerDockStation.
    ToolbarGroupInnerLayer
    This layer is used to define the non rectangular surface of a ToolbarGroupDockStation, it means the surface which is really occupied by dockables.
    ToolbarGroupOuterLayer
    Describes the area around a ToolbarGroupDockStation where the user can drop a Dockable into.
    ToolbarSlimDropLayer
    This layer slim the drop area of ToolbarGroupDockStation, as it take into account means an area where no dockable can be dropped into the station.
